==>STEP NUM: 45
==>ACT: west
==>OBSERVATION: Bottom of Stairwell
===========
==>STEP NUM: 46
==>ACT: south
==>OBSERVATION: Anteroom
   Two exits lead from this cavernous room, north and south. The walls drip with wet, forming a huge pool on the floor.
   A crocodile lies half in the pool, gazing at you, with baleful eyes, jaws wide open. Dagger-sharp teeth glint in the torchlight.
===========
==>STEP NUM: 47
==>ACT: south
==>OBSERVATION: You edge past the reptile.

Dungeon
   You sense, rather than see, the rusty skeletons of old cages and torture devices that line the walls of this cavernous room. One flaming torch, high on a wall, casts mad licks of light into the darkness. Passages lead north and west. Set deep in the rocky floor is a closed trapdoor.
   A pair of manacles hangs from iron chains attached high on the wall.
===========
==>STEP NUM: 48
==>ACT: west
==>OBSERVATION: Corner
   This short passage turns from east to north to stop abruptly at an iron door.
===========
==>STEP NUM: 49
==>ACT: north
==>OBSERVATION: Cell
   Hewn from dense rock, the cell is a stagnant burrow. Except for the tiniest glow of light from the torch two rooms away, it is pitch black.
   As you enter, a tall bony man moves out of the darkness. "Papa," you cry, rushing into his arms.
   "Why, hullo, my dear." He hugs you tightly. "Nick certainly took his time about fetching you."
===========
==>STEP NUM: 50
==>ACT: south
==>OBSERVATION: Corner
   Papa enters just a few steps behind you.
===========
==>STEP NUM: 51
==>ACT: east
==>OBSERVATION: Dungeon
   Papa follows you.
===========
==>STEP NUM: 52
==>ACT: north
==>OBSERVATION: Anteroom
   The crocodile lies half in the pool, sleeping.
   Papa mutters something to himself. You hear an occasional "Zounds!"
   Your father stops, smiling at the crocodile, "Hello, chum, how are you?" He bends over the creature, and scratches its bumpy snout, muttering, "Never seen you sleep like this before." It stirs to life as your father walks over to you by the north entrance. The reptile, waking, lunges after him, choking on its chain.
===========
