Ballroom
   A fashionably bewigged man stalks up to you and bows deeply. "Will you dance?" he asks, with a light French accent. "Not that you have much choice. If you turn me down, your father dies."
===========
==>STEP NUM: 59
==>ACT: north
==>OBSERVATION: "How dare you walk away!" Lafond grips your arm, so you may not leave the floor.
   "So you know I am not your father's friend," Lafond says, offering a hand for the promenade. "Unfortunately, you are in my power, the Falcon is with my dragoons and I am still King of these waters." A gold ring flashes on his hand. It seems vaguely familiar.
